        "18": {
          "id": "18",
          "speaker": "Gale",
          "text": "If it did - perhaps it would understand the weight of what it's asking of us. And why we might seek an alternative.",
          "context": "NodeContext: 'what else we're capable of giving' referring to the possibility of sacrificing himself for the good of all. He's talking about what a mind flayer probably doesn't understand about humans - the capacity for self-sacrifice.",
