                  "link": "43",
                  "is_end": false,
                  "node_type": "normal",
                  "children": {
                    "39": {
                      "id": "39",
                      "speaker": "Gale",
                      "text": "With its power, I could put an end to this whole thing - Crown, Netherbrain, Absolute. Everything.",
